{"tid":180632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣學運占立法院領導者22人判無罪 地院認有「正當行使公民不服從」理由","createTime":"2017-03-31T04:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T05:00:32.000Z","uid":35790,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be6e244cd47d9f77f2ef6e7412eca0031d9e2d31","tid":180632,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"學運占立法院無罪 地院認「正當行使公民不服從」<br />\n<br />\n2017-03-31 12:29<br />\n<br />\n〔記者張文川／台北報導〕2014年引爆太陽花學運的「318攻占立法院行動」，林飛帆、陳為廷、黃國昌等22名被起訴指控煽惑犯罪、妨害公務等罪的被告，今獲台北地院宣判全都無罪，北院發布的新聞稿已全文上網，內容指出主要判決理由，包括，「帆廷昌」等人沒有煽惑他人犯罪的客觀行為與主觀犯意，進入立法院並非「無故」，而是有「行使公民不服從」的正當理由，因此判無罪。<br />\n<br />\n台北地方法院新聞稿全文如下：<br />\n(判詞太長唔貼 自已入去睇) <br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2022329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2022329&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIczOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=3ef91a17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2022329&h=474e98ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2022329</a>"},{"pid":"fc8c19404962df460d1298801a8427af58f60e71","tid":180632,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1d52971e04e6b0b738ec2baa970a80a1b5df13","tid":180632,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"反台撚有咩好講"},{"pid":"5a356973f8dbf4cabd4b0224542bbbc24e45db09","tid":180632,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php96ORMh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php96ORMh.jpg&h=106e1a6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a918f926284759f5444a6bbef44471a8ac33138c","tid":180632,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219c31c0c8abbf5b3f73ccebb591ecfc7d718e62","tid":180632,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/7iUCbV4SE1Q/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F7iUCbV4SE1Q%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=c9aabdb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a78ed6f47f06a232d224e5814aa4e2828fab414","tid":180632,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8e6cc0a02b3c19cd8f509d0140d42d873412d4","tid":180632,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:16:21.000Z","msg":"咩人執政  法院就係咩人  如果仲係國叱黨一定被判有罪"},{"pid":"6c665a25d8d98c3a083232aac281411a5897c40e","tid":180632,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩人執政  法院就係咩人  如果仲係國叱黨一定被判有罪</blockquote><br />\n但台灣人話法院係國民黨開"},{"pid":"823bd0cdbb49bd867e0dfbc64bc965378c1fcb68","tid":180632,"uid":16873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:25:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩人執政  法院就係咩人  如果仲係國叱黨一定被判有罪</blockquote><br />\n馬英九都無罪啦<br />\n選擇性失明？"},{"pid":"51cce698ffe6908a152e727463d74deacbec3508","tid":180632,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:55:10.000Z","msg":"【法院認證】「公民不服從」不違法　理由有這7點<br />\n<br />\n2017/03/31 12:44&nbsp;19271<br />\n<br />\n2014年3月18日學運領袖林飛帆、陳為廷等人，為抗議立法院草率審查《服貿協議》率群眾佔領立法院，引發318太陽花學運，事後，林飛帆、陳為廷、立委黃國昌等22人，被台北地檢署依違反《集會遊行法》、煽惑他人犯罪等罪起訴。台北地院歷經2年多審理，今天上午11時判黃國昌等22人全部無罪。北院行政庭長廖建瑜說明，本次無罪判決的主要依據，就是國內首次使用的「公民不服從」概念。<br />\n<br />\n廖建瑜今天召開記者會指出，台北地院審理318學運佔領立法院案，針對黃國昌等人在抗辯時提出「公民不服從」，也就是德國的抵抗權，有詳加審酌，認為本案是符合公民不服從的概念，有正當事由，不具有實質的違法性。廖建瑜指出，本案法官認定「公民不服從」有7個要件，分別是：<br />\n<br />\n1.抗議對象是與政府或公眾事務有關的重大違法或不義行為<br />\n2.須基於關切公共利益或公眾事務的目的<br />\n3.抗議行為須與抗議對象間具有可得認識的關聯性<br />\n4.須為公開及非暴力行為<br />\n5.須有適當性原則，即抗議手段須有助於訴求目的的達成<br />\n6.須有必要性原則，也就是沒有其他合法、有效的替代手段可以使用<br />\n7.要符合狹義比例原則，也就是抗議行動所造成的危害，須小於訴求目的所帶來的利益，且侷限於最小可能的限度。<br />\n<br />\n法官審理後認為，318太陽花學運佔領立法院案，符合這些要件。<br />\n<br />\n廖建瑜說明，法官指出的「公民不服從」7要件，是依黃國昌等人提供的資料，以及法官另外蒐集的資料，再綜合國內外學說之下，而認定「公民不服從」須有這7要件，這是國內首次使用公民不服從的概念，來認定案件是否具有社會相當性，是否從刑法的角度有非難的必要。（李奕緯／台北報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170331/1088388/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170331%2F1088388%2F&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIczOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=2f8221a6\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170331/1088388/</a>"},{"pid":"ae92051e48e4ad1270047c2ee2fa66040b908359","tid":180632,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T06:08:44.000Z","msg":"柯p 笑9香港垃撚圾，其實都幾合理"},{"pid":"f2d8a0885d933ce08a664cf5ded915f83aa2a8d0","tid":180632,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T06:10:26.000Z","msg":"等睇佔中九子結果"},{"pid":"9771fd8eb0444e5e8ab80eaf7c5a8f9f50ba0750","tid":180632,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:21:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柯p 笑9香港垃撚圾，其實都幾合理</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8678e2593b83e87a7cb433b22ea0f214a6e3ad","tid":180632,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:54:58.000Z","msg":"人地總統 立法院係無篩選全民一人一票選出來"},{"pid":"13436b117c53b85780b7cafaf5a971505aaa34dd","tid":180632,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:10:52.000Z","msg":"革命成功同革命失敗既分別"},{"pid":"6b7cc17fe63c738fef825323e623feafc9f96c42","tid":180632,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:27:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等睇佔中九子結果</blockquote><br />\n呢9條友多數坐，人地台灣就醒目識佔立法院，香港你衝下立法會/政總就比人屌/篤灰/叫停，現在台灣判果陣睇埋呢點:「7.要符合狹義比例原則，也就是抗議行動所造成的危害，須小於訴求目的所帶來的利益，且侷限於最小可能的限度。」，你香港大型佔路同人地佔政府機構比，其實無得比。"},{"pid":"eb76ea1034a39ac8eb9b8ff2a1afe6c611f3c849","tid":180632,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>等睇佔中九子結果</blockquote><br />\n呢9條友多數坐，人地台灣就醒目識佔立法院，香港你衝下立法會/政總就比人屌/篤灰/叫停，現在台灣判果陣睇埋呢點:「7.要符合狹義比例原則，也就是抗議行動所造成的危害，須小於訴求目的所帶來的利益，且侷限於最小可能的限度。」，你香港大型佔路同人地佔政府機構比，其實無得比。</blockquote><br />\n香港係法家法治 <br />\n無西方法治精神"},{"pid":"d3961a2387525d35d90a41eb136509c0cc9c0279","tid":180632,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22713635343265158f3cc769309a7513f29e1ccf","tid":180632,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:20:32.000Z","msg":"taiwan no.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3c49ec015466bda6172e37f7707fe0c90bd3b7","tid":180632,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:03:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>taiwan no.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5760ca487a37e43c047ebf6aaea50a4e8953f0","tid":180632,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:24:46.000Z","msg":"咁先體現到人地係三權分立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7cb18ddff9fdfe9bb3a546d000b0ca908264a85","tid":180632,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:25:01.000Z","msg":"香港：<br />\n<img src=\"http://120.img.pp.sohu.com/images/blog/2008/2/5/23/28/118879af8e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F120.img.pp.sohu.com%2Fimages%2Fblog%2F2008%2F2%2F5%2F23%2F28%2F118879af8e3.jpg&h=c0385128&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c349af9366f923df39d68dc0882c311110de1d3c","tid":180632,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇下H~K幾垃圾"},{"pid":"b2049062c6d3d1c27b908237e6a6348c8032f002","tid":180632,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>革命成功同革命失敗既分別</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣太陽花同香港雨革無分別, 都係成班和理非 坐係到<br />\n<br />\n不過台灣是民主國家, 可以選民進黨上台, 然後宣佈示威者無罪<br />\n但香港由中共話事, 所以示威者一定定罪<br />\n<br />\n根本唔關成功,失敗既事<br />\n<br />\n如果調番轉, 香港有民主, 可以選公民黨上台<br />\n到時雨革示威者一樣可以無罪"}]}